WEBVTT

02:07.710 --> 02:08.520
You're here.

02:09.120 --> 02:10.870
You really know how to enjoy yourself.

02:10.870 --> 02:11.530
Have a seat.

02:14.030 --> 02:14.560
Try this.

02:14.560 --> 02:15.960
It arrived this morning.

02:18.870 --> 02:21.079
Are we really going to be locked up here?

02:21.310 --> 02:23.000
Is there no other way out?

02:23.280 --> 02:25.240
I can't think of any other way for now.

02:25.240 --> 02:26.280
Instead of thinking about that,

02:26.280 --> 02:27.240
we might as well

02:27.240 --> 02:28.640
fill our stomachs first.

02:29.000 --> 02:31.400
You're really good at comforting yourself.

02:31.400 --> 02:33.079
Instead of feeling sorry for yourself,

02:33.079 --> 02:35.010
think about something wonderful.

02:36.630 --> 02:37.960
What wonderful things?

02:39.430 --> 02:41.560
I think right now is pretty wonderful.

02:42.910 --> 02:44.240
Right now is wonderful?

02:46.360 --> 02:47.150
Yeah.

02:48.280 --> 02:49.870
The villagers are all saved.

02:49.870 --> 02:51.400
We've returned safely.

02:51.470 --> 02:52.400
Isn't that good?

02:55.800 --> 02:57.360
If we can get out,

02:57.520 --> 02:58.520
what do you want to do?

02:58.520 --> 03:00.080
The incident in Huangpi Village

03:00.080 --> 03:02.210
showed me the suffering of the people.

03:02.240 --> 03:03.870
If I could open a clinic,

03:04.120 --> 03:06.280
I would definitely be able
to save more people.

03:06.280 --> 03:06.910
Yeah.

03:08.680 --> 03:10.010
That sounds quite nice.

03:10.430 --> 03:12.120
What's the use of it being nice?

03:12.120 --> 03:13.680
Being stuck here now,

03:13.840 --> 03:16.570
thinking or worrying
about anything is useless.

03:27.430 --> 03:28.310
You drank it?

03:30.030 --> 03:30.890
Don't swallow.

03:34.520 --> 03:35.310
Wine.

03:39.560 --> 03:40.160
Calm down.

03:42.710 --> 03:43.240
Don't!

03:50.630 --> 03:51.630
Don't.

03:59.240 --> 04:00.440
Don't, don't, don't.

04:00.840 --> 04:01.870
Are you tired?

04:02.400 --> 04:03.190
Be good.

04:03.960 --> 04:05.620
Let's go. Let's get some rest.

04:07.000 --> 04:07.600
What's...

04:08.190 --> 04:09.030
What's wrong?

04:12.000 --> 04:12.730
Han Yunling.

04:20.950 --> 04:23.390
Giddy up! Off to battle!

04:25.040 --> 04:26.680
Just one lap.

04:43.000 --> 04:43.800
Han Yunling.

04:46.190 --> 04:47.190
You know what?

04:48.270 --> 04:50.070
This courtyard you hate the most

04:51.600 --> 04:53.680
is the place I dream of the most.

04:57.800 --> 04:59.120
Xiao Chi.

04:59.510 --> 05:00.070
Yeah.

05:07.630 --> 05:09.040
I want to...

06:59.720 --> 07:00.980
What's wrong with you?

07:01.270 --> 07:03.510
I got a stiff neck.

07:05.000 --> 07:06.360
Last night,

07:06.950 --> 07:08.480
did I torture you

07:08.480 --> 07:09.270
again?

07:09.600 --> 07:10.390
No.

07:10.560 --> 07:13.070
You just fell asleep
after drinking too much.

07:13.070 --> 07:14.930
I made some congee for you. Try it.

07:19.070 --> 07:20.330
Isn't this burnt rice?

07:20.870 --> 07:21.310
It's just

07:21.310 --> 07:23.310
some dry congee.

07:23.310 --> 07:24.510
It's okay. It's okay.

07:25.190 --> 07:26.600
I like burnt rice too.

07:26.800 --> 07:27.830
That's good.

07:27.830 --> 07:29.000
Then try it.

07:35.240 --> 07:36.270
I have some dishes inside.

07:36.270 --> 07:37.830
Let me go check.

07:59.390 --> 08:00.430
You are here.

08:00.830 --> 08:01.960
I came to take a look.

08:03.120 --> 08:03.870
Look.

08:06.560 --> 08:07.920
Just add some water, and it'll be fine.

08:07.920 --> 08:08.870
Add some water.

08:11.270 --> 08:12.270
General Xiao.

08:12.270 --> 08:13.950
Are you sure this

08:13.950 --> 08:15.040
is edible?

08:17.000 --> 08:18.000
Before cooking,

08:18.000 --> 08:19.560
it was definitely edible.

08:19.560 --> 08:20.720
But now,

08:20.720 --> 08:22.450
I think it should still be fine.

08:22.830 --> 08:23.960
It's cooked anyway.

08:24.430 --> 08:25.720
It seems for these few days,

08:25.720 --> 08:27.480
I'll have to take charge of the meals.

08:27.480 --> 08:28.680
Otherwise, I'll either be poisoned

08:28.680 --> 08:29.630
or starved to death by you.

08:29.630 --> 08:30.160
Sure.

08:30.160 --> 08:30.750
I'll be your assistant.

08:30.750 --> 08:31.510
Can you chop vegetables?

08:31.510 --> 08:32.080
I can.

09:18.630 --> 09:20.120
Xiao Chi.

09:20.120 --> 09:21.440
I told you to chop the vegetables,

09:21.440 --> 09:23.150
not murder them.

09:23.270 --> 09:25.440
I might have used a bit too much force.

09:30.840 --> 09:32.480
Just go out first.

09:32.480 --> 09:34.960
Stop making a mess in here.

09:38.150 --> 09:39.360
Just sit here.

09:39.360 --> 09:40.200
Don't move around.

09:40.200 --> 09:40.870
Okay.

09:45.720 --> 09:46.510
I promise

09:46.510 --> 09:47.570
I won't move at all.

09:47.600 --> 09:48.630
I'm watching you.

10:23.910 --> 10:24.870
All the dishes are ready.

10:24.870 --> 10:25.510
Great.

10:26.510 --> 10:28.080
It's just a simple home-cooked meal.

10:28.080 --> 10:29.000
Make do with it.

10:29.000 --> 10:30.460
It's already very hearty.

10:30.600 --> 10:31.960
When I was in the military camp,

10:31.960 --> 10:33.360
we only had canteen food.

10:39.270 --> 10:40.080
Thank you.

10:41.840 --> 10:42.750
Try this.

10:56.480 --> 10:57.240
Your Majesty,

10:57.240 --> 10:58.510
Xiao Chi and Han Yunling

10:58.510 --> 11:00.240
cured the villagers of Huangpi Village.

11:00.240 --> 11:01.840
They are meritorious subjects
who have served the state well.

11:01.840 --> 11:03.480
Why, after returning,

11:03.750 --> 11:05.630
did they end up being grounded?

11:06.600 --> 11:07.480
Lord Fei.

11:07.480 --> 11:09.270
Don’t be such an alarmist.

11:09.320 --> 11:12.120
They returned from that infected village.

11:12.270 --> 11:14.390
We just let them stay at home

11:14.600 --> 11:15.440
temporarily.

11:15.440 --> 11:17.630
How is that being grounded?

11:18.080 --> 11:18.790
Lord Wang,

11:19.080 --> 11:19.870
haven't seen you for a few days.

11:19.870 --> 11:21.000
You truly look radiant

11:21.000 --> 11:22.460
and flushed with success.

11:23.120 --> 11:24.150
Your Majesty,

11:24.150 --> 11:25.360
I think

11:25.360 --> 11:27.240
what Lord Wang said makes sense.

11:27.320 --> 11:28.630
Xiao Chi stayed in Huangpi Village

11:28.630 --> 11:30.120
for many days.

11:30.270 --> 11:32.910
Although the villagers seem cured now,

11:33.200 --> 11:34.910
just in case,

11:35.030 --> 11:36.320
having them stay at home

11:36.320 --> 11:37.720
to avoid contact for a while

11:37.720 --> 11:39.910
is very necessary.

11:40.080 --> 11:40.880
Your Majesty,

11:41.150 --> 11:43.080
I also think it makes a lot of sense.

11:43.080 --> 11:44.080
Lord Fei,

11:44.240 --> 11:45.000
do not waste

11:45.000 --> 11:47.080
Lord Zhang's good intentions.

11:48.390 --> 11:49.670
What you said

11:50.320 --> 11:51.580
is not without reason.

11:51.910 --> 11:54.570
But General Xiao
has made great contributions.

11:55.080 --> 11:56.200
I plan to let him

11:56.440 --> 11:59.200
leave his residence
during my marriage alliance ceremony.

11:59.200 --> 12:01.320
I will personally host
a welcome banquet for him

12:01.320 --> 12:02.910
as a reward.

12:05.200 --> 12:06.270
And that

12:06.270 --> 12:07.150
Physician Han.

12:07.720 --> 12:08.670
She is the one you brought back

12:08.670 --> 12:10.240
from Tianlang Pass?

12:11.480 --> 12:12.480
Your Majesty,

12:12.720 --> 12:13.480
exactly.

12:13.480 --> 12:15.540
It is Han Yunling from Tianlang Pass.

12:15.600 --> 12:16.910
When I have the chance,

12:17.120 --> 12:18.450
I will see her in person.

12:19.120 --> 12:19.910
Yes.

12:21.080 --> 12:22.000
I...

12:22.000 --> 12:23.730
Thank you again, Your Majesty,

12:24.080 --> 12:26.000
for letting me enter the palace once more.

12:26.000 --> 12:28.870
I really couldn't stay at home anymore.

12:29.440 --> 12:31.500
How could I have forgotten about you?

12:32.120 --> 12:34.270
Why did I let you enter the palace?

12:34.790 --> 12:36.720
With the mistakes you made before,

12:37.440 --> 12:39.960
you should reflect on yourself at home.

12:40.790 --> 12:42.190
If there's nothing else,

12:42.480 --> 12:43.680
don't come out again.

12:45.550 --> 12:46.360
Your Majesty.

12:50.510 --> 12:52.200
This...

12:56.910 --> 12:57.870
I'm done.

12:58.240 --> 12:59.510
General Xiao, you wash the dishes.

12:59.510 --> 13:00.120
Me?

13:00.960 --> 13:01.670
What?

13:02.150 --> 13:05.000
You don't even know
how to wash dishes, General Xiao?

13:05.000 --> 13:06.630
How could I not know how to wash dishes?

13:06.630 --> 13:07.230
I'll do it.

13:26.670 --> 13:27.720
What's wrong?

13:29.600 --> 13:30.670
My hand slipped.

13:30.720 --> 13:34.240
Why weren't you more careful?

13:58.790 --> 14:00.910
Xiao Chi, did you do that on purpose?

14:25.120 --> 14:25.510
My...

14:26.480 --> 14:26.960
neck.

14:29.120 --> 14:30.240
Oh.

14:31.790 --> 14:33.550
Go get some rest.

14:33.550 --> 14:34.910
I'll clean it up.

14:34.910 --> 14:36.200
I know.

14:36.200 --> 14:38.400
Don't worry, I'll clean everything up.

14:39.870 --> 14:44.630
By the Mandate of Heaven,
the Emperor decrees:

14:44.630 --> 14:48.910
the 9th day of this month is chosen
as the auspicious day for the grand wedding,

14:48.910 --> 14:53.910
to be officiated by the Ministry of Rites
and the Astronomical Bureau.

14:54.080 --> 14:56.600
This proclamation is hereby
announced to the world.

14:56.600 --> 14:58.720
By Imperial Command.

15:01.080 --> 15:03.270
Xiao Chi and Han Yunling,
accept the decree.

15:03.270 --> 15:04.930
I accept the Imperial Decree.

15:06.270 --> 15:09.080
This time, Xiao Chi and Han Yunling
have done their best to cure the epidemic.

15:09.080 --> 15:10.200
You have made outstanding achievements.

15:10.200 --> 15:11.600
You are truly pillars of the state

15:11.600 --> 15:12.870
and a blessing to the people.

15:12.870 --> 15:14.240
The quarantine period is now over.

15:14.240 --> 15:15.270
The pestilence has dissipated.

15:15.270 --> 15:15.840
Decree:

15:15.840 --> 15:18.600
Xiao Chi and Han Yunling
are to enter the palace immediately

15:18.600 --> 15:20.870
to receive rewards and titles
before the throne.

15:20.870 --> 15:21.720
By Imperial Command.

15:21.720 --> 15:23.510
I accept the decree.

15:27.910 --> 15:29.270
Alright, please rise.

15:33.630 --> 15:34.760
You're finally out.

15:35.270 --> 15:36.400
There's still time.

15:36.510 --> 15:37.170
His Majesty

15:37.510 --> 15:38.910
has been hoping every day that you could

15:38.910 --> 15:41.080
make it to his marriage alliance ceremony.

15:41.080 --> 15:41.960
Of course.

15:42.080 --> 15:44.280
We will go together when the time comes.

15:47.270 --> 15:48.240
Then I

15:48.440 --> 15:49.970
won't disturb you anymore.

15:50.440 --> 15:51.320
I'll take my leave.

15:51.320 --> 15:51.870
Okay.

15:54.510 --> 15:55.320
Sigh.

15:58.390 --> 15:59.520
Where are you going?

15:59.790 --> 16:00.630
We've been released.

16:00.630 --> 16:01.840
I should hurry up and go.

16:01.840 --> 16:03.840
I've had enough of staying with you.

16:12.080 --> 16:12.750
Jin Xi.

16:12.750 --> 16:13.270
Yes.

16:14.000 --> 16:15.480
Physician Han and General Xiao

16:15.480 --> 16:17.880
have been ground
for almost a month, right?

16:18.910 --> 16:20.570
It's exactly one month today.

16:21.840 --> 16:22.840
It's been so long.

16:23.240 --> 16:24.790
If I were locked up for this long,

16:24.790 --> 16:26.590
I don't know what I would become.

16:28.840 --> 16:30.480
You would look like me now.

16:32.080 --> 16:32.940
Physician Han.

16:33.510 --> 16:35.040
Greetings, Your Highness.

16:35.150 --> 16:36.440
When did you get out?

16:36.510 --> 16:37.550
Just now.

16:37.720 --> 16:39.750
I came to see you as soon as I got out.

16:40.240 --> 16:41.600
You must have been bored to death.

16:41.600 --> 16:43.480
Having food and drink was nice.

16:43.630 --> 16:45.000
I was bored out of my mind.

16:45.000 --> 16:47.120
Mainly because of that annoying Xiao Chi.

16:47.120 --> 16:48.200
It was a nightmare.

16:48.750 --> 16:49.280
Let's go.

16:49.320 --> 16:50.200
I have some good food in my room.

16:50.200 --> 16:50.910
Your Highness,

16:50.910 --> 16:51.720
you go first.

16:52.000 --> 16:53.130
I'll find you later.

16:53.790 --> 16:54.240
Okay.

16:57.910 --> 16:58.720
Jin Xi.

17:05.069 --> 17:07.000
This is the medicine
I prepared for you recently.

17:07.000 --> 17:08.680
I hope it helps you.

17:30.270 --> 17:31.200
Father.

17:31.830 --> 17:33.400
Why did you teach me the way

17:33.400 --> 17:35.000
of an emperor back then?

17:36.720 --> 17:38.510
I am a woman.

17:40.070 --> 17:41.790
Even if I never marry,

17:42.920 --> 17:45.250
I have no chance of inheriting the throne.

17:46.070 --> 17:46.920
Father,

17:46.920 --> 17:49.400
why does everyone
in Jinglan listen to you?

17:49.480 --> 17:50.350
Xie,

17:50.590 --> 17:51.720
to govern a country,

17:51.750 --> 17:53.480
you need not only firm methods,

17:53.720 --> 17:55.310
but also flexible wisdom.

17:55.310 --> 17:56.590
Only by coupling firmness with gentleness

17:56.590 --> 17:57.310
can you

17:57.400 --> 17:58.720
stabilize the court.

17:58.920 --> 18:00.270
The way of an emperor

18:00.640 --> 18:01.680
and the art of managing people

18:01.680 --> 18:02.720
lie in balance.

18:02.920 --> 18:03.680
Father,

18:03.680 --> 18:05.240
I also want to be a wise ruler,

18:05.240 --> 18:06.270
just like you.

18:07.480 --> 18:08.510
Do you

18:09.480 --> 18:11.790
want me to assist Liu Chu forever?

18:16.480 --> 18:18.070
What an old fox.

18:27.590 --> 18:28.510
Your Highness,

18:29.510 --> 18:31.510
if Jiang Wanyu enters the palace,

18:31.790 --> 18:33.350
will His Majesty still

18:33.350 --> 18:34.880
listen to you as he does now?

18:37.310 --> 18:38.640
When people grow up,

18:39.400 --> 18:40.880
they won't listen.

18:41.510 --> 18:42.720
Then what

18:43.070 --> 18:44.070
should we do?

18:47.880 --> 18:50.140
As the Eldest Princess of the Liu family,

18:50.880 --> 18:53.280
I must prioritize the family's interests.

18:53.310 --> 18:53.880
It's best

18:54.680 --> 18:56.720
if she can have another child
as soon as possible.

18:56.720 --> 18:58.550
As long as the Liu family's children

18:58.550 --> 19:00.200
are all under my control,

19:01.350 --> 19:03.280
the empire will be secure forever.

19:09.550 --> 19:10.550
Old fox.

19:11.480 --> 19:12.510
Don't forget

19:13.720 --> 19:15.480
I am your daughter.

19:46.640 --> 19:47.500
Your Highness.

19:47.550 --> 19:48.070
Mhm.

19:48.790 --> 19:50.850
The wedding procession has arrived.

20:01.790 --> 20:03.440
The palace isn't like the outside.

20:03.440 --> 20:04.770
Don't run around later.

20:05.480 --> 20:06.270
I know.

20:14.440 --> 20:15.510
The time has come.

20:16.070 --> 20:17.930
Welcome the Princess of Changmo.

21:14.240 --> 21:15.480
The late Emperor decreed:

21:15.480 --> 21:16.920
Beyond the Great Wall,

21:16.920 --> 21:18.320
the King of Mo shall rule.

21:18.590 --> 21:19.880
Within the Great Wall,

21:19.920 --> 21:21.680
the officials of the court shall preside.

21:21.680 --> 21:23.070
It is also decreed

21:23.510 --> 21:24.640
that let the people

21:24.640 --> 21:27.070
farm and weave, or hunt
for their food and clothing.

21:27.070 --> 21:28.480
Families shall not be separated,

21:28.480 --> 21:30.000
rulers and subjects shall live in peace,

21:30.000 --> 21:31.270
and there shall be no tyranny.

21:31.270 --> 21:33.590
Today, our two nations
are united in a peace alliance.

21:33.590 --> 21:35.480
We lay down our arms
from this day forward.

21:35.480 --> 21:38.140
May there be eternal peace
for all generations!

22:26.400 --> 22:27.270
Today

22:27.750 --> 22:29.440
is the marriage alliance ceremony

22:29.440 --> 22:32.750
between me, Liu Chu,
and Princess Jiang Wanyu of Changmo.

22:33.640 --> 22:34.920
From now on,

22:34.920 --> 22:36.680
the two nations will lay down the spear

22:36.680 --> 22:37.880
and open trade.

22:38.790 --> 22:40.030
From today forward,

22:40.310 --> 22:41.270
Jinglan

22:41.270 --> 22:42.240
and Changmo

22:43.030 --> 22:45.000
shall remain friends for generations,

22:45.000 --> 22:46.920
enjoying everlasting peace!

22:47.000 --> 22:49.030
Remain friends for generations,

22:49.030 --> 22:50.920
enjoying everlasting peace.

22:50.920 --> 22:52.830
Remain friends for generations,

22:52.830 --> 22:55.070
enjoying everlasting peace.

22:55.070 --> 22:57.000
Remain friends for generations,

22:57.000 --> 22:59.070
enjoying everlasting peace.

22:59.510 --> 23:00.370
Your Highness.

23:00.960 --> 23:02.110
He is really looking more and more

23:02.110 --> 23:03.200
like an emperor.

23:04.880 --> 23:05.680
Indeed.

23:06.510 --> 23:09.030
His Majesty is looking more
and more like the late emperor.

23:09.030 --> 23:10.890
Remain friends for generations,

23:10.920 --> 23:12.510
enjoying everlasting peace.

23:12.510 --> 23:15.030
If Father could see this scene today,

23:17.030 --> 23:18.720
he would surely be happy.

23:19.240 --> 23:21.310
Today is His Majesty's big day.

23:21.510 --> 23:24.000
Would you like to go and join the fun?

23:26.680 --> 23:27.920
Today,

23:28.680 --> 23:30.080
he is the main character.

23:30.510 --> 23:32.830
I won't go and join the fun.

23:42.590 --> 23:44.590
This ceremony really exhausted me.

23:49.030 --> 23:50.200
In Changmo,

23:50.790 --> 23:52.030
even when high-ranking officials
marry off their daughters,

23:52.030 --> 23:54.030
there isn't such a grand spectacle.

23:55.310 --> 23:56.910
It seems my father was right.

23:57.200 --> 23:59.200
Liu Chu really put his heart into it.

24:03.920 --> 24:06.200
I'm going to share a bed with him tonight.

24:10.070 --> 24:12.310
What did my father teach me?

24:14.310 --> 24:16.070
A woman’s virtue comes first.

24:16.310 --> 24:18.200
Her words should be cautious.

24:18.310 --> 24:19.830
Her appearance proper.

24:20.310 --> 24:21.920
The husband leads, the wife follows.

24:21.920 --> 24:23.270
United in heart—

24:23.270 --> 24:24.200
One man guarding the pass

24:24.200 --> 24:25.060
is as good as...

24:25.640 --> 24:26.720
No.

24:27.510 --> 24:28.920
I forgot it all.

24:33.880 --> 24:36.070
Let me have a bite to eat first.

24:55.640 --> 24:57.880
His Majesty arrives!

25:34.960 --> 25:36.030
Today,

25:36.440 --> 25:37.700
you must be exhausted.

25:42.510 --> 25:43.480
According...

25:43.480 --> 25:45.480
According to Jinglan's customs,

25:45.680 --> 25:47.830
we use this ceremonial weighing rod

25:48.110 --> 25:50.310
to lift the bride's veil.

25:55.480 --> 25:56.480
Okay.

26:19.310 --> 26:20.200
Are

26:21.680 --> 26:22.350
you ready?

26:33.270 --> 26:34.130
I'm lifting it.

27:03.510 --> 27:04.590
Why is it you?

27:04.830 --> 27:06.070
Why can't it be me?

27:06.070 --> 27:07.440
Aren't you General Xiao's—

27:07.440 --> 27:08.310
Older brother.

27:09.160 --> 27:10.110
Xiao Chi

27:10.200 --> 27:11.240
grew up without a mother.

27:11.240 --> 27:12.400
When we were young,

27:12.400 --> 27:14.440
he, Fei Zheng, and I grew up together
in the Prince's Mansion,

27:14.440 --> 27:15.550
and we kowtowed

27:15.550 --> 27:17.080
and became sworn brothers.

27:17.480 --> 27:19.200
Xiao Chi is the third.

27:19.310 --> 27:20.640
Fei Zheng is the second.

27:20.720 --> 27:21.780
And I am the eldest.

27:22.240 --> 27:23.030
I didn't lie to you,

27:23.030 --> 27:23.830
did I?

27:24.240 --> 27:26.500
No wonder you wouldn't tell me your name.

27:38.920 --> 27:40.550
Then tell me

27:41.030 --> 27:42.240
now,

27:43.640 --> 27:44.590
what is my name?

27:45.270 --> 27:46.240
Liu Chu.

27:50.030 --> 27:51.440
Then tell me,

27:52.680 --> 27:53.590
what am I

27:54.070 --> 27:55.830
to you now?

27:58.000 --> 27:58.880
My husband.

28:02.920 --> 28:04.000
Are you surprised?

28:05.440 --> 28:06.440
No.

28:07.070 --> 28:08.030
It's a shock.

28:12.270 --> 28:13.800
Then let me shock you again.

28:40.920 --> 28:41.720
Your Majesty,

28:42.030 --> 28:44.200
I have an urgent matter to report.

28:52.830 --> 28:53.750
Lord Zhang,

28:54.000 --> 28:55.270
what is it so late at night?

28:55.270 --> 28:56.070
Your Majesty,

28:56.480 --> 28:58.880
this concerns the state.

28:59.000 --> 29:00.880
I dared not delay for a moment.

29:00.960 --> 29:02.960
Since Lord Zhang is looking for you,

29:03.200 --> 29:04.310
you should go.

29:05.310 --> 29:06.070
Alright.

29:06.550 --> 29:07.310
I will

29:07.790 --> 29:08.680
be right back.

29:08.680 --> 29:09.200
Okay.

29:18.070 --> 29:19.640
So he is Liu Chu.

29:23.440 --> 29:24.590
Your Majesty.

29:25.000 --> 29:25.750
Changmo

29:25.750 --> 29:27.240
has sent a letter.

29:27.310 --> 29:29.350
They said that,
since the marriage alliance is complete,

29:29.350 --> 29:31.310
they want to send an envoy

29:31.310 --> 29:32.590
to the capital.

29:32.590 --> 29:33.510
Is that it?

29:35.070 --> 29:36.200
Then let them come.

29:37.200 --> 29:39.070
Although the alliance is complete,

29:39.070 --> 29:41.920
our countries have been
at war for many years.

29:42.310 --> 29:44.110
Even if they come to pay tribute,

29:44.510 --> 29:45.960
it must follow the proper procedures

29:45.960 --> 29:47.880
and be carefully planned.

29:48.790 --> 29:50.310
So what do you suggest?

29:52.030 --> 29:53.290
I request Your Majesty

29:53.480 --> 29:56.540
to move to the Imperial Study
to discuss this in detail.

29:58.640 --> 29:59.830
I know

30:00.270 --> 30:03.070
tonight is Your Majesty's big day,

30:03.070 --> 30:04.800
and I shouldn't be saying this.

30:05.070 --> 30:05.830
But

30:06.240 --> 30:08.110
the country comes first.

30:09.070 --> 30:10.640
I believe Your Majesty

30:10.640 --> 30:12.030
can understand.

30:12.640 --> 30:13.830
Lord Zhang is right.

30:14.110 --> 30:15.840
Let's go to the Imperial Study.

30:38.680 --> 30:40.610
On the left is the Imperial Garden.

30:41.030 --> 30:43.090
On the right is the Imperial Kitchen.

30:45.590 --> 30:47.250
In the northwest corner is...

30:47.680 --> 30:49.880
Behind it is the Emperor's bedchamber.

31:04.110 --> 31:04.920
Who is there?

31:13.920 --> 31:14.920
Commander.

31:15.440 --> 31:16.750
In the middle of the night,

31:16.750 --> 31:18.150
what are you looking for?

31:18.750 --> 31:19.680
It's Lord Fei.

31:20.310 --> 31:22.960
I just saw a shadow flash by.

31:32.200 --> 31:33.590
There's nothing here.

31:34.440 --> 31:35.310
Commander,

31:35.640 --> 31:36.680
you must be seeing things.
